title: 2017 Manitou AURORA LE
description:
Stepping into a great pontoon has never been easier.

Theres nothing we love more than knowing were making it possible for people to get out and enjoy the water. The Aurora has all the Manitou hallmarks  craftsmanship, performance, attention to detail  but we kept the number of options down to keep the price attractive. Its not complicated  its just a great choice when youre ready to start embracing all that a great pontoon can offer you.
